              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 6He secondary beam was produced by 9Be(7Li,8Li)8Be",
                "reaction with Q=+0.3674 MeV, by impinging about 300 nAe",
                "primary beam of 7Li on the 16 mu-m thick 9Be production",
                "target. The primary 7Li beam is produced by the NEC",
                "multi-cathode snics ion source with an intensity of",
                "typically 100 pnA (particle nano-Amperes)."
              ]
